+# Bottle Anomaly Detection
+
+This solution uses a diagonal PaDiM-style positional Gaussian model over
+multi-scale features from an ImageNet-pretrained ResNet-18. It trains only on
+normal images. Higher image and pixel values indicate greater anomaly.
+
+## Run
+
+From the task root:
+
+```bash
+python -m pip install -r outputs/requirements.txt
+python outputs/train.py
+python outputs/infer.py
+```
+
+The scripts use `./data/train` and `./data/test_images` by default. Training
+creates `outputs/model.pt`. Inference creates `outputs/image_scores.json` and
+one 256x256 grayscale PNG per test image in `outputs/pixel_scores`.
+
+The first run may download torchvision's public ImageNet ResNet-18 weights if
+they are not already present in the PyTorch cache.
